'''Indoor Geolocation''' is the process of finding [[geolocation]] of an electronic device inside a building. Since technologies used for indoor geolocation are substantially different from other technologies used for outdoor [[geolocation]] this area is considered as a separate area of science and technology.{{ref|indoor}}
